name: Beige Crochet Lace Tablecloth
description:
This handmade tablecloth is a touch of elegance to your modern decor.  Crocheted with 100%  cotton in natural beige, it can be easily washed.  Made for an oblong  dining table that seats eight people, this piece is perfect for your home, store, or wedding.  It has been starched to hold it's beautiful shape. 

Free standard shipping within the United States.
